      • subscribe

        public void subscribe()
               throws NSException
        API for requesting subscription of Notification service This API should be called with a valid Provider object obtained from Discovery callback. The API should not be called when the Provider is in STOPPED state. Discovery APIs to discover Providers are as below. Start/rescanProvider for D2D, enableRemoteService for D2S,
        Throws:
        NSException - failure to subscribe

      • unsubscribe

        public void unsubscribe()
                 throws NSException

        Throws:
